    Reader modules.
    pt.ua.tm.neji.sentence
    Modules to perform sentence splitting.
    pt.ua.tm.neji.statistics
    Modules and helpers to collect statistics regarding concepts in a corpus or corpora.

    Temporary applications for testing, under development and/or sporadic execution.

    Writer modules.
